    Scenario Outline: Method calls
		Given the expression <expr>
		When I parse it with the full parser
		Then the parse tree should become <tree>

	Examples:
      | expr                                   | tree                                                                  | notes |
      | "1.+(2)"                               | [:do, [:callm, 1, :+, [2]]]                                           |       |
